profile_positions.description:
As a part of the Finance Shared Services of TomTom the GL Margin accounting team looks after the subsidy requests, correct accounting, control and reconciliation of inbound, outbound royalty and revenue & cost of sales flows and manages relationships with all related business partners, both internal and external.

Detailed tasks:
• Coordinate with project manager in order to apply for a subsidy; 
• Coordinate with project managers to have a complete administration (project and timesheets); 
• Send the subsidy documentation to the agencies; 
• Coordinate with external consultants for subsidy management; 
• Maintain the royalty vendor depository; 
• Monitoring and accounting for the inventory processes; 
• Managing internal costs between the Business units and Product units; 
• Create monthly  reporting regarding subsidies and margin activities; 
• Perform monthly account reconciliations for subsidy and margin specific accounts; 
• Prepare monthly accrual journal entries; 
• Conduct work in compliance to royalty contracts, policies and procedures; 
• Research and respond to Business inquiries; 
• Setting up accounting flow for new businesses/projects; 
• Support process and system re-engineering projects.
